een\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-square-check-big w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600\"><path d=\"M21 10.5V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12.5\"></path><path d=\"m9 11 3 3L22 4\"></path></svg> 필수 준비물 점검</h3><span class=\"text-[11px] font-black text-rose-500 uppercase tracking-widest animate-pulse\">Required</span></div><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl border transition-all bg-emerald-50/30 dark:bg-emerald-500/5 border-emerald-100/50\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-lg border-2 mt-0.5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-all bg-emerald-500 border-emerald-500 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black leading-tight text-slate-400 line-through\">개인 노트북 (전원 어댑터 포함)</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">실전 코딩 실습을 위해 반드시 지참</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl border transition-all bg-emerald-50/30 dark:bg-emerald-500/5 border-emerald-100/50\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-lg border-2 mt-0.5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-all bg-emerald-500 border-emerald-500 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-3 h-3\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black leading-tight text-slate-400 line-through\">GitHub 계정 생성 및 로그인 확인</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">코드 저장 및 협업을 위해 필수</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl border transition-all bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-white/5 border-slate-100/50\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-lg border-2 mt-0.5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-all border-slate-200 bg-white\"></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black leading-tight text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200\">Chrome 브라우저 최신버전 설치</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">최적의 실습 환경 보장</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-2xl border transition-all bg-slate-50/50 dark:bg-white/5 border-slate-100/50\"><div class=\"w-5 h-5 rounded-lg border-2 mt-0.5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-all border-slate-200 bg-white\"></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><p class=\"text-sm font-black leading-tight text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200\">AI 서비스(Claude/ChatGPT) 가입</p><p class=\"text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400\">실습 시 사용할 주력 도구</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 to-indigo-950 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 text-white shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden group\"><div class=\"absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-indigo-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-1000\"></div><div class=\"space-y-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"w-14 h-14 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 border border-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-play w-8 h-8\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polygon points=\"10 8 16 12 10 16 10 8\"></polygon></svg></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black tracking-tight\">1분 빠른 체험</h3><p class=\"text-xs font-medium text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\">교육 전 AI의 파워를 경험해보세요.<br/>&quot;나도 할 수 있다&quot;는 자신감이 시작입니다.</p></div><button class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-black text-indigo-400 group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\">체험 시작하기 <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></button></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 border border-slate-200 dark:border-white/5 shadow-sm space-y-8\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-black text-slate-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight flex items-center gap-3\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-save w-6 h-6 text-indigo-600\"><path d=\"M15.2 3a2 2 0 0 1 1.4.6l3.8 3.8a2 2 0 0 1 .6 1.4V19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M17 21v-7a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H8a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v7\"></path><path d=\"M7 3v4a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h7\"></path></svg> 내 결과물 기록</h3><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4\"><div class=\"p-5 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/10 flex items-center justify-between group cursor-pointer hover:border-indigo-300 transition-all\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w